                <h3 class="approach-title">Form Follows Function</h3>
                <p class="approach-description">
                    Beauty emerges from utility. Every design element must serve a purpose, with no ornamental excess. The object's function dictates its form.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="approach-number">02</div>
                <h3 class="approach-title">Truth to Materials</h3>
                <p class="approach-description">
