                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="approach-number">03</div>
                <h3 class="approach-title">Unity of Arts</h3>
                <p class="approach-description">
                    No hierarchy between fine art and craft. Painters, sculptors, architects, and craftspeople collaborate as equals in creating total works of art.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="approach-item">
                <div class="approach-number">04</div>
                <h3 class="approach-title">Social Reform Through Design</h3>
